%% auth — session lifecycle state diagram
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Active: POST /login (session created)
    Active --> Active: POST /refresh (new access token)
    Active --> Revoked: POST /logout
    Active --> Revoked: admin PATCH /users (role/perm change)
    Active --> Revoked: admin DELETE /sessions/{id}
    Active --> Expired: expires_at passed
    Revoked --> [*]: next /me -> 401
    Expired --> [*]: next /me -> 401
